-- HUDController (LocalScript in StarterPlayerScripts)
-- Drives ALL UI feedback:
--   - Showstopper charge bar scaling
--   - Charge-full flash
--   - Ability cooldown overlays with countdown text
--   - Reward pop-ups (+XP / +Coins)
--   - Role reveal splash screen
--   - Trend Tracker banner for Critics
--   - 75% WARNING banner for Designers
--   - Exit waypoint billboard
--   - Strike display (Relevance Meter)
--   - Elimination banner
--   - Device-aware keybind hints
--   - Blind screen for Critics hit by camera flash
--   - Camera shake on hairspray hit
--   - Explosion VFX and poof VFX spawning
--   - Dazed animation playback for blinded critics
--   - Podium spawn/despawn VFX dispatch
--   - SabotagePing: Alert for Critics when sabotaged racks are grabbed
--   - RackStateChanged: VFX + Sound for sabotage/restore toggle

